FBIS4-35591 "drnes106_n_94008" FBIS-NES-94-106 Daily Report 26 May 1994 LEBANON Hizballah TV Breaks Ban on Political Programs Hizballah TV Breaks Ban on Political Programs NC0206093894 Beirut AL-DIYAR in Arabic 26 May 94 p 6 NC0206093894 Beirut AL-DIYAR Arabic BFN [Report by Hasan Darwish from Ba'labakk] [Text] The Al-Fajr television station, which belongs to Hizballah, and the Sky television station, which belongs to 'Abdallah al-Husayni, brother of former Speaker Husayn al-Husayni, yesterday violated the Lebanese cabinet decision that bans the broadcast of news bulletins and political programs. At 2045 yesterday, the two stations, which transmit from Ba'labakk, broadcast the full 15-minute recording of the news conference held by Hizballah Secretary General Hasan Nasrallah.
